  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "My Home Dream is the first simulation game in which the player can create a home of his own, setting up room layouts, walls, garden, etc on a grid using a simple input system. You can choose from a lot of different furnitures, floor tiles, roofs, doors, windows, electronics, etc.\n\nThere are different kind of styles, house and furnitures so anyone can be an inside decorator of bathrooms, kitchens, bedrooms, etc.",
